# BookNook — PDF Reader Application

> Enterprise-grade PDF Book Reader built with Next.js 16, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS

## ✅ Build Status

**Build: ✅ PASSING** — All TypeScript checks pass, static generation succeeds for all routes.

**Dev Server: ✅ RUNNING** — `http://localhost:3000`

---

## 📁 Architecture

```
src/
├── app/                        # Next.js App Router pages
│   ├── layout.tsx              # Root layout with fonts, ThemeProvider, Toast
│   ├── page.tsx                # Home/upload page
│   ├── reader/page.tsx         # Main reader page
│   └── globals.css             # Complete design system (1147 lines)
│
├── features/                   # Feature-based modules
│   ├── upload/                 # PDF upload feature
│   │   ├── components/         # UploadZone, FilePreview
│   │   ├── hooks/              # useFileUpload
│   │   └── types.ts
│   ├── reader/                 # PDF reading feature
│   │   ├── components/         # ReaderLayout, PageCanvas, Toolbar, etc.
│   │   ├── hooks/              # usePDF, useZoom, useFullscreen, etc.
│   │   └── types.ts
│   ├── settings/               # Theme & font settings
│   │   ├── components/         # SettingsPanel, ThemeSelector, FontSizeControl
│   │   ├── hooks/              # useReaderSettings
│   │   └── types.ts
│   └── progress/               # Phase 3 placeholder
│
├── store/                      # Zustand state management
│   ├── pdfStore.ts             # PDF file, page, zoom state
│   ├── settingsStore.ts        # Theme, font size, focus mode
│   └── progressStore.ts        # Reading progress & toasts
│
├── components/                 # Shared UI components
│   ├── ui/                     # Button, Toast, Spinner, Tooltip
│   └── layout/                 # Header, ThemeProvider
│
├── lib/                        # Utility libraries
│   ├── pdf.ts                  # PDF.js lazy-loaded wrapper
│   ├── storage.ts              # localStorage helpers
│   └── constants.ts            # App-wide constants
│
├── config/                     # Configuration
│   ├── theme.ts                # Theme color tokens (4 themes)
│   ├── shortcuts.ts            # Keyboard shortcut definitions
│   └── fonts.ts                # Next.js Google Fonts config
│
└── types/                      # Shared TypeScript types
    └── index.ts
```

