## 🎨 Design System

- **Typography**: Playfair Display (headings), Lora (body), Source Serif 4 (serif UI)
- **Themes**: Light, Dark (default), Sepia, Night — all via CSS custom properties
- **Colors**: 24 CSS custom properties per theme, managed via [ThemeProvider](file:///d:/book-reader/src/components/layout/ThemeProvider.tsx#8-44)
- **Icons**: Lucide React (line icons)
- **Animations**: CSS-only transitions with cubic-bezier easing
- **Responsive**: Mobile < 768px, Tablet 768–1024px, Desktop > 1024px

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
cd d:\book-reader
npm run dev        # Start dev server at http://localhost:3000
npm run build      # Production build
```

## 📦 Dependencies

- `next@16.2.1` — Framework
- `react@19.2.4` — UI library
- `zustand` — State management (3 stores)
- `pdfjs-dist@5.5.207` — PDF rendering (lazy-loaded, CDN worker)
- `lucide-react` — Icons

## 🔮 Future Phases

The `features/progress/` directory is ready for Phase 3. New features simply add a folder under `features/` with their own components, hooks, and types.
